column5: Rent this beautiful home built in 2015! It's in the new section of the subdivision. The house has 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. It is a one and a half story home with 2300 sq ft in total. The house is on a corner lot located in Conroe, TX, about 10 minutes drive to The Woodlands or Lake Conroe. Please let me know if you are interested. Thanks for looking!
column8: Rent a Home! Built 2015! Corner lot!
